      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Mayor Pratt has signed the new\nfranchise for the Washington\nWater Power company in Lidger-\nwood.\n\n\nThe company today filed their\nwritten acceptance of the fran\nchise and work will now begin on\nthe new lines on Addison and Di-\nvision streets within so days.\n\n\nSurveyors have already gone to\nwork On the new lines, which will\nextend from Liberty avenue to\nRowan avenue, over a mile and a\nhalf each."
